release.name: v0.1.0
release.body:
Updates in this release:

* aa80394 Ignore .bowerrc in bower.json (fixes #18)
* f8a5184 Rename runner.html to index.html (Fixes #22)
* ce983b3 Fixes #23 - adds test and tests to ignore field.
* 99c8f6d Remove element name from Polymer()
* 2b971ac Bumped Polymer version
* 8f098bf audit license headers
* 4b14424 Update Polymer to 0.3.4
* c3a6307 Converted DOS file endings to unix
* e4fd909 Added trailing newline to file
* 309d523 Fixed encoding of file
* 285879c Update example docs with additional support pragmas
* 2ee91f3 Update paths to polymer-test-tools.
* dbf57ee Fix breaking tests, move to polymer-test-tools.
* 913ea46 Add newly tagged test tools.

pull_request.title: Broken Link Fix
pull_request.body:
Fixed a broken link in "Add properties and methods" section.

"When you’re creating a new element, you’ll often need to expose a *public API* so users can configure it." 

Current link is: [public API](/polymer/polymer.html#published-properties) >> http://www.polymer-project.org/polymer/polymer.html#published-properties
Correct link is: [public API](docs/polymer/polymer.html#published-properties) >> http://www.polymer-project.org/docs/polymer/polymer.html#published-properties

issue.title: UTF-8 BOM in various files
issue.body:
Having cloned the tutorial, `less finished/index.html` gives:

    <U+FEFF><!doctype html>
    <html>
 
    ...

From what I've seen, the starter `index.html` has this too, but I haven't investigated further.
